Stay]]\n| next_year     = 1998\n| misc = {{External music video|{{YouTube|iIyZKk3-E1w|\"One\" (Perfecto 7\")}}\n | type = single\n}}\n}}\n\nBritish [[Soul music|soul]] singer [[Mica Paris]] released a cover of \"One\" in 1995.<ref name=\"MicaDiscogs\">{{cite web |url=http://www.discogs.com/Mica-Paris-One/master/99969 |title=Mica Paris \u2013 One at Discogs |work=[[Discogs]] |accessdate=23 October 2012}}</ref>\n\nHer version debuted and peaked at number twenty-nine on the [[UK Singles Chart]] on 8 April 1995. It spent a total of four weeks on the chart.\n\n===Track listing===\n'''CD single'''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.discogs.com/Mica-Paris-One/release/525646|title=Mica Paris \u2013 One (CD) at Discogs |work=[[Discogs]] |accessdate=23 October 2012}}</ref>\n{{tracklist\n|extra_column=Producer\n|title1=One\n|length1= 4:30\n|lyrics1=Bono\n|extra1={{flatlist|\n* [[Paul Oakenfold]]\n* [[Steve Osborne]]\n|note1=Perfecto 7\"\n}}\n|title2=One\n|length2= 4:37\n|lyrics2=Bono\n|extra2= [[Mike Peden]]\n|note2=Original Mix\n|title3=One\n|length3= 5:59\n|lyrics3=Bono\n|extra3={{flatlist|\n* Paul Oakenfold\n* Steve Osborne\n}}\n|note3=Perfecto Mix\n|title4=One\n|length4= 5:01\n|note4=Ethnic Boyz Mix\n|lyrics4=Bono\n|extra4=Ethnic Boyz\n|title5=One\n|length5= 7:48\n|note5=Perfecto Dub\n|lyrics5=Bono\n|extra5={{flatlist|\n* Paul Oakenfold\n* Steve Osborne\n}}\n}}\n\n'''Vinyl'''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.discogs.com/Mica-Paris-One/release/167894|title=Mica Paris \u2013 One (Vinyl) at Discogs |work=[[Discogs]] |accessdate=23 October 2012}}</ref>\n{{tracklist\n|collapsed=yes\n|headline= Side one\n|extra_column=Producer\n|title1=One\n|length1= 4:30\n|lyrics1=Bono\n|extra1={{flatlist|\n* Paul Oakenfold\n* Steve Osborne\n}}\n|note1=Perfecto Mix\n|title2=One\n|length2= 4:37\n|lyrics2=Bono\n|extra2= Mike Peden\n|note2=Original Mix\n}}\n{{tracklist\n|collapsed=yes\n|headline= Side two\n|extra_column=Producer\n|title1=One\n|length1= 5:01\n|note1=Ethnic Boyz Mix\n|lyrics1=Bono\n|extra